== Welcome to the SproutCore Todo's Sample

This is a fork of step 5 of the todos application.
The idea behind this fork is to focus on some GUI components usage, datasource usage, and other advanced usages.

The idea is that we augment the tutorial and add to it.

As we learn to do new things, we add them to the tutorial.

My hope is that these ideas can be added upon and shared.

My hope is to grow the sproutcore community and learn more about sproutcore in the process.


